title: Episode 138: The Legend (Feat. John Legend & Jasmine Sanders)
itunes:title: Episode 138: The Legend (Feat. John Legend & Jasmine Sanders)
description:
On this weeks episode, John Legend sits with the ladies of Lip Service and addresses Kanye West posting their text conversation on social media. John breaks down his own sex playlist he would make with Chrissy, what he would call his own porno, and much more! Shouts to our girl Jasmine Sanders for coming through as a special guest host!
